---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import LinkList from "../../components/LinkList.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import hero from "../../assets/mobiller-shots.png";
import styleguide from "../../assets/mobiller-styleguide.png";
import mobillerOne from "../../assets/mobiller-1.png";
import mobillerTwo from "../../assets/mobiller-2.png";
import mobillerThree from "../../assets/mobiller-3.png";
import icon from "../../assets/mobiller-icon.png";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="MoBiller by Michael Dijkstra"
  pageDescription="MoBiller by Michael Dijkstra"
  logo="true"
  bodyClass="bg-[#252525] text-white font-sans"
>
  <div class="space-y-24 py-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl text-9xl leading-24 mx-auto space-y-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl leading-16 lg:leading-24">MoBiller</h1>

      <div class="w-full border-white/80 p-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <Picture
          class="block w-full max-w-full h-auto"
          src={hero}
          alt="MoBiller app screenshots"
        />
        <figcaption class="text-2xl mt-3">a. MoBiller screens</figcaption>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-24">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl">VMO Medical billing, made easy.</h2>
          <p class="text-2xl">
            MoBiller is an iOS app that streamlines capturing patient details,
            recording billing codes, and generating billing reports.
          </p>

          <p class="text-2xl">
            I began by prototyping the core features with React Native and Expo,
            which allowed for rapid iteration and early user testing. A key
            focus during this phase was ensuring the app could reliably scan and
            parse patient sticker details, as this functionality formed the
            backbone of the workflow. Validating this early meant I could refine
            the experience before committing to the full design.
          </p>

          <p class="text-2xl">
            After the prototype was proven, I moved into a detailed design phase
            using Figma. I focused on creating an interface that felt simple and
            familiar for clinicians, with clear typography and intuitive
            navigation. The design phase also defined key components and
            patterns that would later form the foundation of the appâ€™s design
            system.
          </p>

          <p class="text-2xl">
            With the design finalised, I returned to development using React
            Native to build out the full application. I implemented Unistyles to
            establish a consistent design system and ensure the visual language
            carried through across every screen. This final phase brought
            together the validated workflows and polished design into a
            productionâ€‘ready build.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-12">
            <h3 class="text-3xl">Project Gallery</h3>

            <div>
              <Picture
                class="block w-full max-w-full h-auto"
                src={mobillerOne}
                alt="MoBiller app screenshots"
              />
              <figcaption class="text-2xl mt-3">b. App screens</figcaption>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Picture
                class="block w-full max-w-full h-auto"
                src={mobillerTwo}
                alt="MoBiller app screenshots"
              />
              <figcaption class="text-2xl mt-3">
                c. Interaction design
              </figcaption>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Picture
                class="block w-full max-w-full h-auto"
                src={mobillerThree}
                alt="MoBiller app screenshots"
              />
              <figcaption class="text-2xl mt-3">d. App screens</figcaption>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Picture
                class="block w-full max-w-full h-auto"
                src={icon}
                alt="MoBiller icon design"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <figcaption class="text-2xl mt-3">e. App icon</figcaption>
            </div>

            <div>
              <Picture
                class="block w-full max-w-full h-auto"
                src={styleguide}
                alt="Screenshot of styleguide"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <figcaption class="text-2xl mt-3">f. Styleguide</figcaption>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-4 space-y-6 md:sticky">
          <dl class="grid grid-cols-4 text-2xl">
            <dt class="col-span-1">Scope</dt>
            <dd class="col-span-3">
              <ul class="list-none">
                <li>Visual Design</li>
                <lli>Wireframing</lli>
                <li>Prototyping</li>
                <li>Development</li>
                <li>Design System</li>
              </ul>
            </dd>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-4xl">
            <span class="-ml-1 pr-4">ðŸ‘‡</span> Up next
          </h2>
        </div>

        <LinkList
          links={[
            {
              url: "/work/climate-salad",
              title: "Climate Salad",
              description: "View case study",
            },
            {
              url: "/work",
              title: "Work",
              description: "See my full project list and work history.",
            },
            {
              url: "/contact",
              title: "Contact",
              description: "Have a project to discuss? Get in touch.",
            },
          ]}
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    :root {
      --nav-rgb: 37, 37, 37;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
